{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"41":"Types of Blood-Wit (Kitab Al-Diyat)"},"section_detail":{"41":{"hadithnumber_first":4494,"hadithnumber_last":4595,"arabicnumber_first":4494,"arabicnumber_last":4595}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":4580,"arabicnumber":4580,"text":"। আশ-শা‘বী (রহঃ) সূত্রে বর্ণিত। তিনি বলেন, আল-গুররাহ হলো পাঁচশ দিরহাম। ইমাম আবূ দাঊদ (রহঃ) বলেন, রাবী‘আহ বলেছেন, গুররাহ হলো পাঁচশ দীনার।[1] সনদ দুর্বল।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif Isnaad Maqtu"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Daif Isnaad Maqtu"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":41,"hadith":87}}]}